{"type":"message","id":"8783acf5","parentId":"45329915","timestamp":"2026-03-27T23:34:07.524Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session is the current cron session itself. The last message in the session is from the assistant (me). There are no user messages in the last 5 minutes from other sessions. So there are no active conversations from users.\n\nI should proceed with the autonomous learning task: search for latest trends in enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services - industries related to 道简网络 (Daojian Network).\n\nLet me search for the latest information in these areas.","thinkingSignature":"2641add10a284130fec995939e58049328efd95b232479bcfbce8ff5f1ed9fd8"},{"type":"text","text":"没有活跃对话，开始自主学习。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_096wzytkakja_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"搜索道简网络相关行业的最新动态，整理3-5条关键信息并保存到 /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md\n\n请搜索以下几个主题的最新资讯（2026年3月）：\n1. 企业数字化转型最新政策/动态\n2. 智能安防行业动态\n3. 网络系统集成/弱电工程趋势\n4. IT运维服务行业动态\n\n搜索完成后，整理3-5条最有价值的信息，以以下格式保存：\n\n# 学习笔记\n\n## 日期：2026-03-28\n\n## 行业动态摘要\n\n1. **【标题】**\n   - 内容摘要...\n   - 来源...\n\n（每条信息要包含标题、摘要、来源）\n\n注意事项：\n- 优先选择与中国市场、To B企业服务相关的动态\n- 选择对道简网络有参考价值的商业/技术趋势\n- 保存文件时如果目录不存在需要先创建","label":"行业动态自主学习","runtime":"subagent","runTimeoutSeconds":180,"mode":"run"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":821,"output":369,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45171,"cost":{"input":0.00024629999999999997,"output":0.0004428,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0020085299999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774654434882}}
