{"type":"message","id":"e449443b","parentId":"5e42aa9e","timestamp":"2026-03-27T23:34:15.025Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The sub-agent has been spawned and will run the autonomous learning task. I should let the cron job know the task has been accepted.","thinkingSignature":"e9882994ef8f2df340d424aa1ad7778299a795a3c2a8eb889f060fe9c9bf247f"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n检测到空闲状态，已启动自主学习子任务。\n\n**执行情况：**\n- ✅ 无活跃对话（最近5分钟内无用户消息）\n- ✅ 已派发子Agent搜索行业动态（企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务）\n- ⏳ 子任务运行中，预计180秒内完成\n\n子任务完成后会将学习笔记保存至 `/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md`。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1292,"output":129,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45402,"cost":{"input":0.0003876,"output":0.0001548,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0018618299999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774654450327}}
